{"id": 1303, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你做过的最正确的一笔投资是什么？", "description": "我今年最大的收益是，租的那套房子，每平米售价由3万涨到了5万……（题图来自：Sophia Foster-Dimino）", "record_count": 2769, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161101163208pfaGH9ZRJgBCck84.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-03T03:19:53Z", "options": [{"id": 129792, "content": "诸事不顺啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805558}, {"id": 130048, "content": "离开了那份死气沉沉的工作 离开了那个敏感小心眼的女人 进了医院做了小手术 远离了那个口若悬河的人 走进了自己预设的轨道 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583616}, {"id": 129793, "content": "多看了几本书", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753654}, {"id": 130049, "content": "按时吃药。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 129794, "content": "多看了几本书", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753654}, {"id": 130050, "content": "健身了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162124}, {"id": 129795, "content": "有一份很舒服的感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794516}, {"id": 130051, "content": "健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819897}, {"id": 134148, "content": "蚂蚁借呗  去学跳舞?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834713}, {"id": 134404, "content": "在读研和工作中做了一个目前认为很满意的决定", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830523}, {"id": 129796, "content": "申请到出国学习机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816537}, {"id": 130052, "content": "和心爱的老婆囍结婚啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819898}, {"id": 129797, "content": "舍弃买廉价淘宝衣服的购物观念，开始学会购买质量佳的衣服；\n学会提前消费，不因钱不够而放弃自己当期要买的东西。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782813}, {"id": 130053, "content": "学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649398}, {"id": 131846, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679825}, {"id": 129798, "content": "买书", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816830}, {"id": 130054, "content": "貌似没有，难受", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819900}, {"id": 129799, "content": "国债逆回购……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817338}, {"id": 130055, "content": "成功增重了15斤，又开始去健身房减肥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799509}, {"id": 135176, "content": "对体重大大投资,高回报:-)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839302}, {"id": 129800, "content": "换了份工作，节省了生活成本和时间，有更多时间陪家人和做自己的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819134}, {"id": 129801, "content": "买了一套房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819136}, {"id": 129802, "content": "健身锻炼", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817797}, {"id": 130058, "content": "配了个新镜头，从此找不到理由推脱器材?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475482}, {"id": 134667, "content": "买房吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836717}, {"id": 129803, "content": "学了喜欢的乐器", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543857}, {"id": 129804, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330854}, {"id": 130060, "content": "卖了手机买了手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819942}, {"id": 129805, "content": "自学语言 读很多书 分手 护肤 嗯 这都是我要做的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817630}, {"id": 130061, "content": "为了喜欢一个人而认真读书，减肥，护肤……最后，他不知道我爱他，但我将得到更好的我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819724}, {"id": 129806, "content": "补办四级证书，办了张信用卡?。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445872}, {"id": 130062, "content": "额……学化妆？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686426}, {"id": 129807, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259532}, {"id": 130063, "content": "和朋友合伙做生意", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817647}, {"id": 129808, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819149}, {"id": 130064, "content": "买个更大的行李箱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367330}, {"id": 132113, "content": "上大学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826748}, {"id": 129809, "content": "离开父母，换了个全新的城市来生活，每个月的工资一半交了房租，月光但是很满足", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664975}, {"id": 130065, "content": "去年买了房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819974}, {"id": 130066, "content": "找个姑娘过生日", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673397}, {"id": 129811, "content": "谈了一段恋爱很美好哈哈哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819162}, {"id": 130067, "content": "给自己投资", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486970}, {"id": 130068, "content": "唉，还在啃老的我没资格谈投资", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641365}, {"id": 148757, "content": "饭上我爱豆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883935}, {"id": 129813, "content": "读书，健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814662}, {"id": 130069, "content": "没有去追女生?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790842}, {"id": 